---
title: Tri-Color Quinoa Salad with Apple, Eggplant, and Honey Vinaigrette
description: This salad has autumn written all over it thanks to the combination of Honeycrisp apples, crunchy walnuts, and tart cranberries. Protein-packed quinoa adds some bulk, and a sweet sherry honey vinaigrette brings it all together.
